entries.title: Dantooine System: Destroy the Black Sun Assassin
entries.split_quest_alert: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 We have the opportunity to take out a second target.  Proceed to Lok Space as fast as possible. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.quest_target_d: A ruthless Black Sun Assassin linked to a number of attacks on Naboo citizens
entries.quest_location_d: An area in the Dantooine System
entries.quest_escort_d: Secondary objectives, destroy at all costs.
entries.failed_escape: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 Beldini has escaped! This spells dark times for our Diplomatic Corps. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.escort_wiped_out: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 All escort craft have been destroyed. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.escort_remaining: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 An escort craft has been destroyed, %DI remain \#pcontrast3 >
entries.destroy_escort: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 Great job, now finish off his escort. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.assassinate_success: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 Beldini has been destroyed!  The Diplomatic Corps has one less assassin to fear now. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.arrival_phase_2: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: \#pcontrast1 Beldini's craft has dropped from hyperspace.  Transmitting his location now. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.arrival_phase_1: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 Beldini will be in the sector shorly, stand by for coordinates. \#pcontrast3 >
